				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">that's the problem
<br />

<br />
It's becoming apparent they do not PLAY the game, certainly not at high level.
<br />

<br />
Aggro from PoP nukes is STUPID STUPID STUPID, what do  have to do to get across that this is major BAD thing? We've been pointing out our problems for ages but they are *NOT* being *listened* to. The developers are busy trying to work on things, they have limited budgets etc, this I understand, but it DOESN'T excuse not being able to *comprehend* what is being SAID by the mage players.
<br />

<br />
Damn single shot calliav isn't worth a flying ****. This MSIV won't aggro worth crap, wtf good is it? I'll either die or it will.
<br />

<br />
Either make the frikkin pet aggro like a SOB, or WIPE the mage class and give us equivalent wizards. I didnt play a mage all this time to be a "nuker" with a graphical dot. To quote Gandalf:<span style="font-weight: bold"> "I AM NOT SOME CHEAP CONJUROR OF TRICKS!"</span>
<br />

<br />
I'm PO'd really freakin' PO'd. I pay money to have fun, NOT have a gigantic whinefest and conflict. I'm known for having the patience of a rock but ENOUGH IS ENOUGH.
<br />

<br />
Why is it EQOA mages are GOOD, but ordinary EQ mages SUCK BALLS now, hm? Yes I know our capabilities, but these are no longer balanced by our detractors.
<br />

<br />
--Mages were not SUPPOSED to die more often than shamans on raids.
<br />
--Mages were meant to have a pet as a defence, IT'S NO DAMN USE NOW!
<br />
--Why is the epic pet far better than any of the other ones in regards to aggro or damage on mobs &lt;lvl 61, wouldn't happen to be the other pets SUCK in comparison, hm?
<br />
--Look at how pet and nuke damage has scaled up, In PoP it went massively nuke orientated, we are *NOT* wizards, the aggro problems are part of this.
<br />
--We dont have any self preservation devices, so if our pets don't work, either give us runes, snares roots and stuns, or wipe the mage class entirely because SONY hasn't the balls or the brains to fix it.
<br />
--Putting mobs with see invis all over zones and nerfing COH there means those zones cannot be traversed or others aided by mages, who cannot Crowd Control anyway, ergo WTF IS THE POINT OF HAVING MAGES THERE AT ALL?!
<br />

<br />
Yes I am well aware no class is perfect, but enough is *ENOUGH*. This is not a case of wanting to be "THE uber-noob class", but the class is,  FUBARED. (whether Xalmat or Cyricus will agree, cause they are still rational human beings  <img src="images/smiles/icon_lol.gif" alt="Laughing" border="0" /> )
<br />

<br />
How to fix the class?
<br />

<br />
1) Mage pet only, higher lvl pet only summoned weapons proccing snare, rune, stun and slow. This can be done easily alterign exisitng spells...Blade of the Kedge = slow proc 50% Tagars Insects; Blade of Walnan = stun, Fists of ixiblat = proc snare. New spell, Blade of the Rathe procs rune 4. Set proc rates suitable to intended use and game balance.
<br />
Slow will be suitable to AID as a slower, not replace a proper slower.
<br />
Stun is great aggro and useful.
<br />
Snare is great aggro and a great utility (been in many groups with no snarer)
<br />
Rune proc, very useful for pet survivability.
<br />

<br />
2) mage only pet summoned armour equal to Velious armour, and a higher lvl 65 or perhaps ancient spell that summons ornate equivalent.
<br />

<br />
3) Add 3k hp to all mage pets at least. Even with better mitigation tc, Aes getting by Calliavs will still vape them. <span style="font-style: italic">Hi I'm a mage who has 5700hp buffed, and I only have 2 items of Elemental gear, if I had Time gear I'd have 7+k hp, don't you think a 2 ton elemental should be a BIT TOUGHER THAN A WHIMP IN A BATH ROBE?!</span>
<br />

<br />
4) Give mages root AND root items made mage useable.
<br />

<br />
5) Reduce the damage on PoP nukes approximately 200 to 300 hp but give them a -100 resist modifier, this will reduce aggro, but keep good DPs because of less resists and be useful in PVP and on resistant mobs. make Destroy Summoned a true lure -300 resist...it Destroys Summoned things, not give them a tickle up their backsides  <img src="images/smiles/icon_lol.gif" alt="Laughing" border="0" />  
<br />

<br />
6) Take root OFF the fuggin earth pet NOW!! Change it to a powerful snare (ie 70% or more movement reducer). So we can use the earth pet in groups or raids without problems. FIVE BLOODY YEARS we've pointed out root is monkey balls. For those who want root on earth pet, the root portion makes the pet basically unuseable in groups or raids, it also doesnt aggro worth a hoot, screws up aggro for everyone, ruisn ranger damage etc. Earth pet casitng say the 18 sec snare would own, without making us "druids"
<br />

<br />
7) Make the Fire 63 pet cast Lure of Ice, Lure of Fire, Lure of Magic, make it rooted when summoned like servant of ro, cast NO other spells, give it enormous mana, set it's recasting time so that it's DPs is around 10 to 20 higher than lvl 62 water pet from the rear since this fire pet CANNOT tank. make the fire pet lvl 65 and the earth pet lvl 61, air 62 and water 63 to sow how they SHOULD be used. Fire pet should be an elite damage dealerrmostly used on RAIDS, so it wont push, etc.
<br />

<br />
<img src="images/smiles/icon_cool.gif" alt="Cool" border="0" /> Make pets take their masters resists in PvP, stop trying to say it's "imbalanced" compared to oh say, rooting mezzing snaring yer pet like a Qeynos noobie with 0 MR, hm? Or lighting you up with a 9k Harm Touch, my that's balanced compared to what...what do mages do in PVP? Ah, dispel enemies and run around like headless chickens with nerfed pets and nukes, oh sorry nerfed nukes hardly land anyway, oh dear.
<br />

<br />

<br />
Game should be FUN, not a bloody headache, the developers duty is to make a *FUN* game, not a headache where we fell like Oliver Twist saying <span style="font-style: italic">"Please sir, can I have some more gruel?"</span> and feel oh so special after getting things which should have been given to us for FREE in the FIRST place.
<br />
:/
<br />

<br />
SIC BALLS, JIBOBER BUDDY! 
